```plantuml
@startuml andersonkmi_credit-card-bindb-service-aws

actor Client
participant "API Gateway" as APIGW
participant "CSV Processor Lambda" as CSVProc
participant "SQS" as SQS
participant "BIN Processor Lambda" as BINProc
participant "DynamoDB" as DDB

Client -> APIGW: Upload CSV file
APIGW -> CSVProc: Trigger Lambda (S3 event)
CSVProc -> SQS: Split CSV into messages
SQS -> BINProc: Trigger Lambda (SQS event)
BINProc -> DDB: Store processed BIN data
BINProc --> APIGW: Processing confirmation
APIGW --> Client: Success response

@enduml
```